Package: MToolR
Type: Package
Title: Companion package for the Mental Model Mapping Tool M-Tool. https://www.m-tool.org/
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mario Angst, Karlijn van den Broek
Maintainer: Mario Angst <mario.angst@uzh.ch>
Description: This is a companion R package for the Mental Model Mapping Tool M-Tool. 
  https://www.m-tool.org/
  The package provides:
  a) functionality to load and process data generated by M-Tool
  b) procedures for common (basic) analytical tasks
  c) visualization functions
